Package model

Class Measurement

java.lang.Object
model.Measurement
public class Measurement extends Object
The Measurement class represents a single measurement of blood pressure taken from a patient.

  • Constructor Details

    • Measurement

      public Measurement(int id, int sbp, int dbp, LocalDateTime datetime, String informations, String CFpatient)
      Creates a new Measurement with the given id, systolic blood pressure, diastolic blood pressure, date and time, additional information, and the patient's CF code.
      Parameters:
      id - the unique identifier for this measurement
      sbp - the systolic blood pressure reading for this measurement
      dbp - the diastolic blood pressure reading for this measurement
      datetime - the date and time when the measurement was taken
      informations - additional information about the measurement
      CFpatient - the CF code of the patient who took the measurement
